translation[18]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,Haa-meem
  44,2,Qasam hai iss wazahat wali kitab ki
  44,3,Yaqeenan hum ney issay ba-barkat raat mein utara hai be-shak hum daraney walay hain
  44,4,Issi raat mein her aik mazboot kaam ka faisla kiya jata hai
  44,5,Humaray pass say hukum hoker hum hi hain rasool bana ker bhejney walay
  44,6,Aap kay rab ki meharbani say. Wohi hai sunnay wala jannay wala
  44,7,Jo rab hai aasmano ka aur zamin ka aur jo kuch inn kay darmiyan hai agar tum yaqeen kerney walay ho
  44,8,Koi mabood nahi iss kay siwa wohi jilata hai aur maarta hai wohi tumhara rab hai aur tumharay aglay baap dadon ka
  44,9,Bulkay woh shak mein paray khel rahen hain
  44,10,Aap uss din kay muntazir rahen jabkay aasman zahir dhuwan laye ga
  44,11,Jo logon ko gher ley ga yeh dard-naak azab hai
  44,12,Kahen gay kay aey humaray rab! Yeh aafat hum say door ker dey hum eman qabool kertay hain
  44,13,Inn kay liye naseehat kahan hai? Khol khol ker biyan kerney walay payghumber unn kay pass aa chukay
  44,14,Phir bhi inhon ney unn say mun phera aur keh diya kay sikhaya parhaya hua baaoola hai
  44,15,Hum azab ko thora door ker den gay to phir tum apni ussi halat per aajao gay
  44,16,Jiss din hum bari sakht pakar pakaren gay bilyaqeen hum badla lenay walay hain
  44,17,Yaqeenan inn say pehlay hum qom-e-firaon ko (bhi) aazma chukay hain jinn kay pass (Allah ka) ba-izzat rasool aaya
  44,18,Kay Allah Taalaa kay bando ko meray hawalay kerdo yaqeen mano kay mein tumharay liye amanat daar rasool hun